The paper deals with text detection and recognition in natural images, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also introduces a character attention mechanism and uses RNNs for word recognition, which are techniques commonly used in natural language processing (cs.CL). The paper also involves training a unified model for two tasks, which is a problem in machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Finally, the paper involves information retrieval, as it deals with detecting and recognizing text in images (cs.IR).
